  "description": "Let me start by offering a thanks-at-large to the folk who read \u0026amp; shared my post soliciting funds for buying onion \u0026amp; saffron bulbs, and to those who could and did choose to help me exceed that goal! My goal was $155, and $218 ended up being donated. Looking at how much space is available for planting, I\u0026rsquo;m going to go ahead and increase the amount of onions in the order. I mentioned in a subscriber-only update, but I\u0026rsquo;m working to set up a robust digital ledger for my practices, and so hopefully, I can keep y\u0026rsquo;all updated about what comes from this purchase! Reading that sentence back, \u0026ldquo;robust digital ledger,\u0026rdquo; sounds like I\u0026rsquo;m being euphemastic about using a blockchain, and that\u0026rsquo;s not the case; the software being used is Emacs, Org-mode, and Beancount. Anyway, here\u0026rsquo;s what I wrote before checking my email and seeing that y\u0026rsquo;all brought me past my goal:\n",
